data.description: Sweet 2 bedroom/1 bath townhome in Butte Haven with community views of Thumb Butte and easy access to restaurants, golf, hiking and more. This great room concept has a roomy dining area with double-door storage/pantry with a family room and bonus area that is perfect area for an office, art, craft or exercise. The split bedrooms create a private retreat for everyone.Fenced back patio is a wonderful outdoor living area of your creation. Community has a pool and clubhouse.  HOA maintains common areas, townhouse exterior maintenance and includes water, sewer, trash. This one can be yours! See it today.
